extends layout

block content
    div(class="textBody")

        div(class="section")

            h1(class="heading large")   Staying in Albuquerque
            p(class="textBlock")
                | For our guests, we reccomend one of two options for your stay
                | in Albuquerque.  <br /><br /> There are a limited number of rooms available
                | at Los Poblanos, and if you're interested you can check availability
                | by contacting them.  <br /><br /> Second, we have blocked out rooms at the Sheraton
                | Albuquerque Uptown.  <br /><br /> If you choose to stay at the Sheraton, we will
                | provide transport to and from the ceremony and reception for all of our
                | guests. <br /> <br /> Guests are responsible for transportation from the Airport to
                | the hotel of their choosing.

        div(class="section")

            h1(class="heading large")   Los Poblanos Organic Farm
            p(class="textBlock")
                | Our ceremony and reception will be held at Los Poblanos Organic Farm,
                | and Los Poblanos has a handful of rooms available for varying rates.
                | All of the rooms are luxurious, and include complementary gourmet breakfast and
                | full access to the grounds.  <br /><br /> This is perfect if you're interested in
                | being surrounded by nature and want to feel separated from the city.
                | Los Poblanos will provide a calm and relaxing experience.  Rooms start at
                | $156 a night and go up from there.

            p(class="textBlock")
                | If you would like more information about Los Poblanos, please visit their
                | Accommodations page <a href="http://www.lospoblanos.com/accommodations/" target="#">here or call (505) 344-9297.</a>
                | Please mention the Steiling-Woody wedding if you would like to book so we
                | know how many of our guests are staying there.

        div(class="section")
            h1(class="heading large")   Sheraton Albuquerque Uptown
            p(class="textBlock")
                | We have arranged for a block of rooms at the <a href="http://www.starwoodmeeting.com/Book/STEILINGWOODYWEDDING" target="#">Sheraton Albuquerque Uptown</a>.  This hotel is
                | located near an outdoor shopping mall and various restraunts and bars.  <br /><br />  For any guests staying
                | at the Sheraton, we will provide a shuttle to and from the ceremony on Saturday night.  <br /> <br />
                | The hotel offers a complimentary shuttle that will take you to <a href="http://www.simon.com/mall/abq-uptown" target="#">The Shops at ABQ Uptown</a>.
                | <br /><br /> If you would like to book, please visit <a href="https://www.starwoodmeeting.com/Book/STEILINGWOODYWEDDING" target="#">this site</a> or call (505) 881-0000 and mention that you are part of the Steiling-Woody
                | wedding to get a deal of $89.00 a night.


    script
        $(document).ready(function (){
            $('#accommodations').addClass('selected').removeClass('unselected');
        });
